GET http://localhost:4321/authors?page=1&size=5

### Recuperar una author por id
GET http://localhost:4321/authors/2

###
POST http://localhost:4321/authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Isabel",
  "nationality": "mexicana",
  "birthDay": "1942-08-02"
}

###
DELETE http://localhost:4321/authors/4

### Actualizar un author
